      "expert_verified": false,
      "extraction_notes": "Rule defines the auspicious (Saumya) or inauspicious (Krura) nature of specific Shashtyamsa divisions (D60) based on whether the sign is odd or even. The list of Krura Shashtyamsas for odd signs is explicitly provided, with the rule for even signs being a reversal of this classification."
